  "title": "Embedded Software Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>[Job ID: 1111074] </strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Design, develop, and maintain machine control and process control software for automated semiconductor equipment.</li><li>Integrate software modules, OEM equipment, and hardware components into fully functional, reliable systems.</li><li>Produce high-quality, optimized, and testable code; perform debugging, enhancements, and participate in design and code reviews.</li><li>Plan, execute, and document software validation, regression testing, and performance testing in compliance with SEMI SECS/GEM standards.</li><li>Collaborate with cross-functional teams and support on-site installation, commissioning, upgrades, and customer field service activities.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>5 years of experience in software design, development, and validation within Windows environments (Windows XP and above).</li><li>Strong proficiency in C++, VC++, MFC, SQL, object-oriented programming, and multi-threaded control software.</li><li>Experience with hardware integration (servo/stepper motion controllers, analog devices, high-speed I/O).</li><li>Solid understanding of the full software development life cycle (SDLC) and software quality assurance processes.</li></ul><p><strong>Added Advantages</strong></p><ul><li>Familiarity with SEMI SECS/GEM standards.</li><li>Experience in GUI development, C#, and WPF.</li><li>Knowledge of scripting languages such as Python or VBA.</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. However, rest assured that all applications will be updated to our resume bank for future opportunities.</p><p>Please kindly refer to the Privacy Policy of Good Job Creations for your reference: https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Ong Kang Quan Ryan<br />EA Personnel Registration Number: R23116952<br />EA License No.: 07C5771</p>",
